---
title: Sweet-Soy Beef, Tofu & Greens Poke Bowl with Sriracha Mayonnaise & Pickled Cucumber
description: We love poke bowls because they’re so easy to customise with your favourite flavours. This veggie version uses marinated tofu, Asian greens and cucumber, with a sprinkle of sesame seeds to tie the whole thing together.
